Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Add bin subfolder

In order for binary targets to build bin must exist, so add it to the
repo and remove it from the package's .gitignore.

Signed-off-by: Jose Lamego <jose.a.lamego@intel.com>
---
 .gitignore     | 1 -
 bin/.gitignore | 1 +
 2 files changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)
 create mode 100644 bin/.gitignore

diff --git a/.gitignore b/.gitignore
index 3df128b9..1673977b 100644
--- a/.gitignore
+++ b/.gitignore
@@ -9,7 +9,6 @@
 *.o
 *.orig
 /pause/pause.o
-/bin/
 /test/bin2img/bin2img
 /test/checkseccomp/checkseccomp
 /test/copyimg/copyimg
diff --git a/bin/.gitignore b/bin/.gitignore
new file mode 100644
index 00000000..f935021a
--- /dev/null
+++ b/bin/.gitignore
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+!.gitignore
